Format: <type>/<slug>
- Lowercase only
- Kebab-case slug (hyphen-separated words)
- No spaces, no special characters except hyphens and forward slash
{{- if .Detailed}}
- Slug should be descriptive and capture the full intent (up to 6 words)
{{- else}}
- Slug should be the shortest possible meaningful name (2-4 words)
{{- end}}

Example output: feat/add-user-auth

{{- if .Explain}}
Output the branch name on the first line, then a blank line, then a line starting with "Reasoning:" explaining your choice.
{{- else}}
